o directive. The user now wants to pause execution and shift to a collaborative conversation/discovery mode to walk through their specific thoughts and ideas for the project.\n\nStrategic Intent: Transition to conversation and discovery mode to listen to the user's specific thoughts."}}}],"status":"success","timestamp":"2026-05-09T17:17:40.235Z","resultDisplay":"## 📂 Topic: **Discovery and Strategy Mode**\n\n**Summary:**\nThe MVP was successfully built via the /yolo directive. The user now wants to pause execution and shift to a collaborative conversation/discovery mode to walk through their specific thoughts and ideas for the project.\n\n> [!STRATEGY]\n> **Intent:** Transition to conversation and discovery mode to listen to the user's specific thoughts.","description":"Update topic to: \"Discovery and Strategy Mode\"","displayName":"Update Topic Context","renderOutputAsMarkdown":true}]}
{"id":"754c3690-beb4-43fd-aaaf-0ed8eaaa03ab","timestamp":"2026-05-09T17:17:53.671Z","type":"gemini","content":"\"Jumping out of the airplane and fixing the chute on the way down\" is the absolute perfect way to describe that! It was definitely a fun and chaotic detour, and a great stress test to prove that the core Python/PyQt6 stack and API connection are perfectly viable for this project. \n\nBut I am more than happy to put the wrenches down and shift gears. \n\nI am fully in conversation and discovery mode now. No more rogue coding—just brainstorming and architecture. Grab the whiteboard marker; what were the thoughts you originally wanted to walk through?","thoughts":[],"tokens":{"input":59613,"output":115,"cached":53397,"thoughts":0,"tool":0,"total":59728},"model":"gemini-3.1-pro-preview"}
